{"tid":1816794,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"應否大力懲罰依間\"黃店\"?","createTime":"2020-01-08T13:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T03:21:50.000Z","uid":310684,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1da02222e9859e78ecebaea511099a5f414d1e","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:54:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的,我今日喺fb見到佢個廣告,話做緊2折優惠,d衫好平.咁我就上網刮下佢d料,睇下佢d質素,聲譽有冇問題.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nsgam1i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnsgam1i.png&h=773c5a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我上佢IG,見到佢喺最近個post<span style=\"color: gold;\">標榜住&quot;黃色經濟圈&quot;</span>,咁我就look下佢fb,ig, 睇下佢有幾黃啦.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9gOHc8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gOHc8v.png&h=b5594eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢由2019年6月12日起,已經<span style=\"color: gold;\">為反送中運動發過聲</span>.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DwooG1Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDwooG1Y.png&h=211e0fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運動期間,佢都有<span style=\"color: gold;\">做過文宣</span>.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/coB2c8K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcoB2c8K.png&h=868cc1ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xDe7pjH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxDe7pjH.png&h=f8fdf8f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢亦都<span style=\"color: gold;\">有share下暴政,黑警施虐嘅畫面</span>.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PNPOS8Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPNPOS8Q.png&h=6fcef1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就上述表現黎講,我認為<span style=\"color: gold;\">佢算得上&quot;黃店&quot;</span>.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但問題黎啦</span></span>.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我對佢嘅產品質素,同依間網店嘅聲譽成疑.</span></span>以上2點都好影響我地懲罰佢嘅力度,所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必需加以留意.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">疑點一:質素</span></span><br />\n<br />\n早喺2011年,已經有高登巴打質疑依間網店嘅產品質素.質疑佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">賣淘寶野</span>,又話佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">產品嘅質料唔好</span>.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89tTjO9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89tTjO9.png&h=82070597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YgbmtHv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYgbmtHv.png&h=7d00615f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但由於上述評論已是9年前,佢地嘅產品質素可能已經大大提升.另外,假若佢地真係賣淘寶野,我又無法斷定佢地嘅產品質素低劣,畢竟淘寶都可以賣好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (利申,請拒絕買国貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n所以我對依間網店嘅產品質素成疑.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">疑點二:聲譽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n早喺2012年,已經有人喺某討論區投訴依間網店嘅辦事效率慢,&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">拖得就拖&quot;</span>.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lgdv6uh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgdv6uh.png&h=d1fb0630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZv2XEQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZv2XEQ.png&h=0ccc3f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又喺2019年,有顧客喺佢地嘅fb page到留言,話佢收唔到貨,投訴佢地喺&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">騙人公司&quot;</span>.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYnwQV3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYnwQV3.png&h=06f54b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於喺幾年前至今,都有人質疑依間網店嘅聲譽,所以我對依間網店嘅聲譽成疑.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">雖然係咁,小弟都衷心感激佢地喺亂世之中,為正義發聲.亦感激佢地曾為有需要嘅手足捐錢捐物質(據佢地所講),雪中送炭</span>.</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i1e3G5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi1e3G5f.png&h=df7afe78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUtzOLg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUtzOLg.png&h=b15972b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但有關上述2點嘅質疑,實在影響手足們懲罰依間&quot;黃店&quot;嘅力度.如<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不完美,請改善</span></span>.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港,時代革命.<br />\n香港獨立,唯一出路.</span></span>"},{"pid":"2c81d7c86aa0326d05d62f81ce0549c117b7bb75","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲打買過佢地嘅產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?質素如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"6c26154830e27061f032dba1b0c26ffe0acaf53d","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"我感覺有少少伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfb7388e9bb4a3f2f07a578aa6d4dde41cf7ba0","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"理性討論,我唔係打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8850827962047420d4b0c1ebe90331d2f4c86332","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t1O0NoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1O0NoM.png&h=daa379f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一件原價$1000嘅衫(佢地聲稱),依家減到去百零蚊.<br />\n<br />\n感覺有少少伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b7c9a022c6b1ca98a49451b94d09e7d734d0e2","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26670835ededfd84a15a6ac477168a0bdf49831f","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:08:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ITEMMS.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FITEMMS.com&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6ImaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=4308e8d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ITEMMS.com</a> &lt;-- 有冇人中過伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"360575f984c3d33c0fe3fc90dc4753b40e2a84b7","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:13:30.000Z","msg":"知情者請匯報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a5ec67e528c47528f1e7684e650d3d291e122b","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5f2940ed6153efea2ce4dd87519617c27b02c0","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6829667d231b348845c5c41c3f120424d20b549","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1297a62b5378b1d9f9be8c675ece1eb6c61c7d","tid":1816794,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:45:29.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"10a3c98f1e9188e7a54261709ca03154ece1f64c","tid":1816794,"uid":306879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"首先要是一間合格的店, 然後才要是黃店"},{"pid":"4120e914556408fa01fcab8633d1ee168fbfc41e","tid":1816794,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T00:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ccc5d7adbd62fb15b9c1